data.description: Welcome to 16906 Langham Heights Lane in the sought after Langham Creek Estates and close to plenty of shops and amenities! This spacious 5 bed, 2.5 home offers an open floor concept with a beautiful kitchen and a family room combo perfect for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, gas range stove, recess lighting, and a kitchen bar. A huge primary bedroom is located upstairs with an ensuite bathroom boasting a jetted tub and a separate shower, his and her sinks, and an enormous walk in closet with plenty of shelving and space! All secondary bedrooms are spacious as well. The game room is located upstairs and can double as an office or media room. The backyard is nicely sized and has plenty of space for gardening or additions to the home. Solar panels and digital thermostats are included with the sale of the home, making your electricity bill non existent! Water softener and refrigerator included! Schedule your showing!!!
